ina and Marta''\n|1989\n|\n|[[R\u00e1dio e Televis\u00e3o de Portugal|RTP]]\n|based on a novel by [[Camilo Castelo Branco]]\n|-\n|''[[Roseira Brava]]''\n|''Brave Rosebush''\n|1995\n|\n|[[R\u00e1dio e Televis\u00e3o de Portugal|RTP]]\n|by Toz\u00e9 Martinho, Sarah Trigoso and Cristina Aguiar\n|-\n|''[[Saber Amar]]''\n|''Knowing How to Love''\n|2003\n|2003\n|[[Televis\u00e3o Independente|TVI]]\n|Casa da Cria\u00e7\u00e3o and Maria Jo\u00e3o Mira\n|-\n|''[[Santa B\u00e1rbara (telenovela)|Santa B\u00e1rbara]]''\n|''Saint Barbara''\n|2015\n|2016\n|[[Televis\u00e3o Independente|TVI]]\n|Artur Ribeiro, adapted from Mexican original ''[[La Patrona]]''\n|-\n|''[[A Senhora das \u00c1guas]]''\n|''The Lady of the Waters''\n|2001\n|\n|[[R\u00e1dio e Televis\u00e3o de Portugal|RTP]]\n|by Manuel Arouca and Tom\u00e1s M\u00farias\n|-\n|''[[Sonhos Tra\u00eddos]]''\n|''Betrayed Dreams''\n|2002\n|2002\n|[[Televis\u00e3o Independente|TVI]]\n|by Maria Jo\u00e3o Mira and Virg\u00edlio Castelo\n|-\n|''[[Telhados de Vidro]]''\n|''Glass Roofs''\n|1993\n|1993\n|[[Televis\u00e3o Independente|TVI]]\n|by [[Rosa Lobato Faria]]\n|-\n|''[[Tempo de Viver (2006)|Tempo de Viver]]''\n|''Time to Live''\n|2006\n|2007\n|[[Televis\u00e3o Independente|TVI]]\n|Rui Vilhena\n|-\n|''[[Terra M\u00e3e]]''\n|''Motherland''\n|1998\n|\n|[[R\u00e1dio e Televis\u00e3o de Portugal|RTP]]\n|by Rui Vilhena\n|-\n|''[[Todo o Tempo do Mundo]]''\n|''All the Time in the World''\n|1999\n|2000\n|[[Televis\u00e3o Independente|TVI]]\n|by Toz\u00e9 Martinho, Sarah Trigoso and Cristina Aguiar\n|-\n|''[[Tudo Por Amor]]''\n|''Everything for Love''\n|2002\n|2003\n|[[Televis\u00e3o Independente|TVI]]\n|adaptation Texto & Cena\n|-\n|''[[Tu e Eu]]''\n|''You and I''\n|2006\n|2007\n|[[Televis\u00e3o Independente|TVI]]\n|Manuel Arouca and Tom\u00e1s M\u00farias\n|-\n|''[[O \u00daltimo Beijo]]''\n|''The Last Kiss''\n|2002\n|2003\n|[[Televis\u00e3o Independente|TVI]]\n|adaptation by Casa da Cria\u00e7\u00e3o\n|-\n|''[[A \u00danica Mulher]]''\n