 Me, and Baby Makes Two |url=https://archive.nytimes.com/www.nytimes.com/library/film/041798object-film-review.html |website=[[The New York Times]] |accessdate=January 7, 2020 |date= April 17, 1998}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 1999\n| ''[[200 Cigarettes]]''\n| Kevin\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | <ref>{{cite web |first1=Kevin|last1= Thomas |title=Young, Talented Cast Gives a Spark to '200 Cigarettes' |url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1999-feb-26-ca-11777-story.html |website=[[Los Angeles Times]] |accessdate=January 7, 2020 |date= February 26, 1999}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 1999\n| ''{{sortname|The|Cider House Rules|dab=film}}''\n| Wally Worthington\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | <ref>{{cite web |first1=Michael |last1=Wilmington |title='Cider House's Sweet Tale Rules |url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1999-12-17-9912170010-story.html |website=[[Chicago Tribune]] |accessdate=January 7, 2020 |date= December 17, 1999}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2000\n| ''[[Gen-Y Cops]]''\n| Ian Curtis\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | <ref>{{cite web |first1=Angelica|last1= Xidias |title=The embarrassing movie roles celebrities want you to forget |url=https://www.vogue.com.au/culture/features/the-movie-roles-celebrities-want-you-to-forget/image-gallery/eae0e9f90552b72c5fa03dccdc2a5d3d |website=[[Vogue (magazine)|Vogue Australia]] |accessdate=January 7, 2020|language=en |date= March 26, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2001\n| ''[[Wet Hot American Summer]]''\n| Andy\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | <ref>{{cite web |first1=Clark |last1=Collis |title=Paul Rudd remembers 'Wet Hot American Summer' |url=https://ew.com/article/2011/06/27/paul-rudd-wet-hot-american-summer/ |website=[[Entertainment Weekly]] |accessdate=January 7, 2020 |language=en |date= June 27, 2011}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2001\n| ''On the Edge''\n| Dr. Kenneth Grearly\n| Short film; Segment: \"Reaching Normal\"\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | <ref>{{cit