]]''\n| Alvin\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | <ref>{{cite web |first1=Lindsey |last1=Bahr |title=Paul Rudd and Emile Hirsch in 'Prince Avalanche' -- EXCLUSIVE POSTER |url=https://ew.com/article/2013/06/21/prince-avalanche-poster/ |website=[[Entertainment Weekly]] |accessdate=January 15, 2020 |date=21 June 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2013\n| ''[[This Is the End]]''\n| Himself\n| Cameo\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" |  <ref name=Insider />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2013\n| ''[[All Is Bright]]''\n| Rene\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | <ref name=Insider />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2013\n| ''[[Anchorman 2: The Legend Continues]]''\n| Brian Fantana\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | <ref name=Insider />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2014\n| ''[[They Came Together]]''\n| Joel\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | <ref>{{cite web |first1=Manohla |last1=Dargis |title=When Boy Meets Girl in Ben Franklin Wigs |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/27/movies/paul-rudd-and-amy-poehler-star-in-they-came-together.html |website=[[The New York Times]] |accessdate=January 15, 2020 |date=26 June 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2015\n| ''[[The Little Prince (2015 film)|The Little Prince]]''\n| Mr. Prince (voice)\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | <ref name=Insider />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2015\n| ''[[Ant-Man (film)|Ant-Man]]''\n| [[Scott Lang (Marvel Cinematic Universe)|Scott Lang / Ant-Man]]\n| Also writer\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | <ref name=\"CinemaBlend\">{{cite web |first1=Gina |last1=Carbone |title=What's Next For Ant-Man After Avengers: Endgame? Kevin Feige Has A Cryptic Answer |url=https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2482148/whats-next-for-ant-man-after-avengers-endgame-kevin-feige-has-a-cryptic-answer |publisher=Cinema Blend |accessdate=January 15, 2020 |date=12 October 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2016\n| ''[[Captain America: Civil War]]''\n| Scott Lang / Ant-Man\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\" | <ref name=\"CinemaBlend\" />\n|-\n! sco