rect-to-video\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[Dishdogz]]''\n| Tony<ref name=\"Dishdogz\">{{cite web |title=Dishdogz |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dishdogz/ |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=March 5, 2019}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[The Sandlot: Heading Home]]''\n| Tommy \"Santa\" Santorelli<ref name=\"TCM\" />\n| Direct-to-video\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Alice Upside Down]]''\n| Ben McKinley<ref name=\"TCM\" />\n|\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''\u00c4ntligen midsommar!''\n| Sam<ref name=\"TCM\" />\n|\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''Upstairs''\n| Ward Weaver<ref name=\"Upstairs 2009\">{{cite web |title=Upstairs 2009 |url=https://filmow.com/upstairs-t33219/ |website=Filmow |accessdate=March 5, 2019}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''Silent Venom''\n| Lt. Comdr. James O'Neill<ref name=\"TCM\" />\n| Direct-to-video\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''Sam Steele and the Junior Detective Agency''\n| The Cat<ref name=\"Sam Steele and the Junior Detective Agency\">{{cite web |title=Sam Steele and the Junior Detective Agency |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sam_steele_and_the_junior_detective_agency |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=March 5, 2019}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[Redemption Road]]''\n| Boyd<ref name=\"TCM\" />\n|\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[The Final Storm (film)|The Final Storm]]''\n| Silas Hendershot<ref name=\"TCM\" />\n| Direct-to-video\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''Hanna's Gold''\n| Cole<ref name=\"Hanna's Gold\">{{cite web |title=Hanna's Gold |url=https://www.barnesandnoble.com/w/dvd-hannas-gold-luke-perry/22373635 |website=Barnes & Noble |accessdate=March 5, 2019}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[Good Intentions (2010 film)|Good Intentions]]''\n| Chester Milford<ref name=\"TCM\" />\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Red Wing (film)|Red Wing]]''\n| Carl Blanton<ref name=\"TCM\" />\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''Scoot and Kassie\u2019s Christmas Adventure''\n| Paul Stevenson<ref name=\"TCM\" />\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''Beat Beneath My Feet''\n| Max Stone<ref name=\"TCM\" />\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| \u2018\u2018A Fine Step\u2019\u2019\n| Cal Masterson \n|\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''Dudes & Dragons''\n| Lorash<ref name=\"TCM\" />\n| \n|-\n| 2018\n| ''The Griddle House''\n| Older Jack\n|\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Once Upon a Time in Hollywood]]''\n| [[Wayne Maunder]]<ref name=\"TCM\" />\n| Posthumous release\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[Voyagers!]]''\n| Union Prisoner<ref name=\"Luke Perry, Star of 90210 and Riverdale, Dies at 52\">{{cite web |last1=Bradley |first1=Laura |title=Luke Perry, Star of 90210 and Riverdale, Dies at 52 |url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2019/03/luke-perry-obit |website=Vanity Fair |accessdate=March 5, 2019}}</ref>\n| Episode: \"The Day the Rebs Took Lincoln\"\n|-\n| 1988\n| ''[[Loving (TV series)|Loving]]''\n| Ned Bates<ref name=\"Remembering Luke Perry: Photos from the Actor's Career Before '90210'\" />\n| Unknown episode\n|-\n| 1988\u20131989\n| ''[[Another World (TV series)|Another World]]''\n| Kenny<ref name=\"TV Guide\">{{cite web |title=Luke Perry List of Movies and TV Shows |url=https://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/luke-perry/credits/163166/ |website=TV Guide |accessdate=March 5, 2019}}</ref>\n| 10 episodes\n|-\n| 1990\u20131995;<br />1998\u20132000\n| ''[[Beverly Hills, 90210]]''\n| [[Dylan McKay]]<ref name=\"TV Guide\" />\n| 199 episodes\n|-\n| 1993\n| ''[[Saturday Night Live]]''\n| Himself (host)\n| Episode: \"[[Saturday Night Live (season 18)#ep338|Luke Perry/Mick Jagger]]\"\n|-\n| 1993\n| ''[[The Simpsons]]''\n| Himself (voice)<ref name=\"TV Guide\" />\n| Episode: \"[[Krusty Gets Kancelled]]\"\n|-\n| 1994\u20131995\n| ''[[Biker Mice from Mars]]''\n| [[Biker Mice from Mars#Recurring characters|Napoleon Brie]] (voice)<ref name=\"Luke Perry, Star of \u201890210\u2019 and \u2018Riverdale,\u2019 Has Died at 52\">{{cite web |last1=Keene |first1=Allison |title=Luke Perry, Star of \u201890210\u2019 and \u2018Riverdale,\u2019 Has Died at 52 |url=http://collider.com/luke-perry-dead/ |website=Collider |accessdat