johnson_county_war |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=March 5, 2019}}</ref>\n| Television film\n|-\n| 2002\u20132004\n| ''[[Jeremiah (TV series)|Jeremiah]]''\n| [[Jeremiah (TV series)#Characters|Jeremiah]]<ref name=\"TV Guide\" />\n| 35 episodes\n|-\n| 2003\n| ''[[Clone High]]''\n| [[Juan Ponce de Le\u00f3n|Ponce de Le\u00f3n]] (voice)<ref name=\"TV Guide\" />\n| Episode: \"Litter Kills - Literally\"\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[Will & Grace]]''<ref name=\"auto\"/>\n| Aaron\n| Episode: \"The Birds & the Bees\"\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[What I Like About You (TV series)|What I Like About You]]''\n| Todd<ref name=\"TV Guide\" />\n| 3 episodes\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[Descent (2005 film)|Descent]]''\n| Dr. Jake Rollins<ref name=\"Descent (2005)\">{{cite web |title=Descent (2005) |url=https://www.allmovie.com/movie/v331212 |website=All Movie |accessdate=March 5, 2019}}</ref>\n| Television film\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[Supernova (2005 film)|Supernova]]''\n| Dr. Chris Richardson<ref name=\"TCM\" />\n| Television film\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''[[Windfall (TV series)|Windfall]]''\n| Peter Schaefer<ref name=\"TV Guide\" />\n| 13 episodes\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Biker Mice from Mars (2006 TV series)|Biker Mice from Mars]]''\n| Napoleon Brie (voice)<ref name=\"Biker Mice from Mars\">{{cite web |title=Biker Mice from Mars |url=http://www.tv.com/shows/biker-mice-from-mars/cast/ |website=TV.com |accessdate=March 5, 2019}}</ref>\n| Episode: \"Once Upon a Time on Earth\"\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[John from Cincinnati]]''\n| [[John from Cincinnati#Cast and characters|Linc Stark]]<ref name=\"TV Guide\" />\n| 10 episodes\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[Law & Order: Special Victims Unit]]''\n| Noah Sibert<ref name=\"TV Guide\" />\n|Episode: \"Trials\"\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[A Gunfighter's Pledge]]''\n| Matt Austin<ref name=\"The Pledge (2008)\" />\n| Television film\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[A Very Merry Daughter of the Bride]]''\n| Charlie<ref name=\"TCM\" />\n| Television film\n|-\n| 2008;<br />2018\n| ''[[Criminal Minds]]''\n| Benjamin Cyrus<ref name=\"