s\">{{cite web|title=SikkemaJenkins&Co:Artists:Jennie C. Jones|url=http://www.sikkemajenkinsco.com/index.php?v=artist&artist=5153403403728|publisher=Sikkema Jenkins & Co|accessdate=15 March 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Awards==\n*Robert Rauschenberg Award, Foundation for Contemporary Arts, 2016<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.foundationforcontemporaryarts.org/recipients/jennie-c-jones|title=Jennie C. Jones :: Foundation for Contemporary Arts|website=www.foundationforcontemporaryarts.org|access-date=2017-02-28}}</ref>\n*Joan Mitchell Award Grantee, 2013\n*The Joyce Alexander Wein Prize, 2012\n*Art Matters Grant, 2012<ref>{{cite web|title=Grantee List|url=http://www.artmattersfoundation.org/grantees/year/two-thousand-seven-to-present|publisher=Art Matters Foundation|access-date=23 February 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150306012649/http://www.artmattersfoundation.org/grantees/year/two-thousand-seven-to-present#|archive-date=2015-03-06|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n*William H. Johnson Prize, 2008\n*Creative Capital Grantee, 2008\n*Pollock-Krasner Grant Recipient, 2000<ref name=BioPDF />\n\n==Collections==\n*BNY Mellon, Pittsburgh, PA\n*Deutsche Bank, New York, NY\n*[[Solomon R. Guggenheim Museum]], New York, NY\n*Mott-Warsh Collection, Flint, MI\n*The Hirshhorn Museum and Sculpture Garden, [[Smithsonian Institution]], Washington, DC\n*The Zimmerli Museum, Rutgers University, New Jersey\n*[[Studio Museum in Harlem|The Studio Museum in Harlem]], New York City, NY\n*[[Los Angeles County Museum of Art]] (LACMA), Los Angeles, CA\n*The Americas Collection, Deutsche Bank\n*Weil, Gotshal & Manges, New York City, NY<ref name=BioPDF />\n*[[Museum of Modern Art]], New York, NY\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.artinamericamagazine.com/reviews/jennie-c-jones/print/ Art in America Review for ''Absorb/Diffuse'' at The Kitchen 2011]\n*[https://www.nytimes.com/2010/07/30/arts/design/30galleries-003.html Ken Johnson's review of ''Electric'' at Sikkema Je